Perfect! Here's the optimal solution approach:

```typescript
import { NgStyle } from '@angular/common';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-style',
  template: `
    <div [ngStyle]="{ 
      'color': textColor,
      'font-size.px': fontSize 
    }">
      Styled text
    </div>
  `,
  standalone: true,
  imports: [NgStyle]
})
export class StyleComponent {
  textColor = 'red';
  fontSize = 20;
}
```

This solution demonstrates best practices for Angular development and shows how to properly implement `[ngStyle]`.

